      <title>啤酒禁令引发赞比亚、刚果边境纠纷，铜出口受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/zambia-congo-start-talks-to-end-spat-that-closed-border-key-to-copper-trade</link>
